msgid ""
"Forgotten your password? Enter your email address below, and we'll send you "
"an email allowing you to reset it."
msgstr ""
"Har du glemt din adgangskode? Indtast din e-mailadresse nedenfor, så sender "
"vi dig en e-mail, hvor du kan nulstille den."

#: templates/account/password_reset.html:26
msgid "Reset My Password"
msgstr "Nulstil adgangskode"

#: templates/account/password_reset.html:31
msgid "Please contact us if you have any trouble resetting your password."
msgstr ""
"Kontakt os venligst, hvis du har problemer med at nulstille din adgangskode."

#: templates/account/password_reset_done.html:16
