#: templates/account/snippets/warn_no_email.html:3
msgid "Warning:"
msgstr "Advarsel:"

#: templates/account/snippets/warn_no_email.html:3
msgid ""
"You currently do not have any email address set up. You should really add an "
"email address so you can receive notifications, reset your password, etc."
msgstr ""
"Du har i øjeblikket ikke oprettet nogen e-mailadresse. Du bør virkelig "
"tilføje en e-mailadresse, så du kan modtage notifikationer, nulstille din "
"adgangskode osv."

